umentation/image/8245f2a0-3cad-425d-98a4-d6468fe1a816?resizing_type=fit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/8245f2a0-3cad-425d-98a4-d6468fe1a816?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=2800&amp;height=799\"><!----><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/8245f2a0-3cad-425d-98a4-d6468fe1a816?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=1400&amp;height=400\"><!----><source media=\"(min-width: 0)\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/8245f2a0-3cad-425d-98a4-d6468fe1a816?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=768&amp;height=219\"><!----><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"figure-img img-fluid\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/8245f2a0-3cad-425d-98a4-d6468fe1a816?resizing_type=fit\" alt=\"Packaging And Shipping Your Mobile Game Banner\" width=\"1920\" height=\"548\" data-caption=\"\"></picture></a><!----><!----><!----></figure></div><!----></block-image><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Phần này chứa các hướng dẫn để xây dựng ứng dụng của bạn, làm việc với mặt tiền cửa hàng và đóng gói iOS và Android.</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><ul block-document-list=\"\" class=\"block-document-list\" ngh=\"11\"><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"10\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:packaging-android-projects-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/52e0dbba-2fd8-493b-ad29-9c57745a46e5